I called and order breakfast from them over an hour ago- nothing has come. Called back, a different woman picked up and accused me of not placing the order ‘& hanging up on the previous woman before she finished “filling out the order”. Which is completely false-I would never rudely hang up on a place where my food will be handled. If I hung up it was because she said “okay” after repeating my order and address back. Then the woman was like “oh well like you’re calling private now- you did before as well-you didn’t give her your number -she couldn’t call you back”. At the point I am done with their lies- my number is normally not shown as “private” they have caller id (I never give them my number when I place an order- so it didn’t cross my mind to do so). If they knew that my number showed private- I should have been asked for my number. Yea, we’re human-she might have forgotten to at that moment-but do NOT have your other co worker rudely accuse me of hanging up on you when I didn’t. As well as speak to me in a condescending matter. -The customer service is terrible here. Go to Loma’s across the street.
